rComments: Best professor I ever had!! Professor Bateson is very caring, her lectures are amazing (I learned so much!!!), the readings are very captivating, groups discussions are really interesting! I spent a wonderful time in her class! The exams are for most of them practical exercises (participant observation, archives research, interview, etc.).

she is such a sweet prof, friendly, cares about her students learning, and pushes deadlines back if you need. pretty easy marker and the assignments are actually pretty interesting! would recommend :)
